                            <h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Renames “items” to “goals”</li>
                                <li>Updates the layout of goals</li>
                                <li>Fixes an issue where burning could be undone</li>
                                <li>Updates the donation links</li>
                                <li>Fixes an issue where alternate Dock icons could be selected without unlocking</li>
                                <li>Includes minor interface improvements</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Known Issues</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>When the list is not scrolled to the top, the burning animation may appear incorrectly</li>
